## âœ… Validation

This implementation has been verified using:
- **FIPS 197 AES core test vectors**
- **NIST SP 800-38A OFB mode vectors** (Section F.4.1 and F.4.2)

Run:

```bash
./nist_test
```

If correct, you will see:
```
âœ… NIST test vector passed.
```

